Create an huggingface account and write your account name                    vars HF_USER
Create an huggingface  token (finegrained or not)                            secrets HF_TOKEN
Create an huggingface  space for Docker                         
Create a grafana cloud account 
create a grafana stack and access it / write down the name of the stack 
es.  https://yourusername.grafana.net/                                       vars GRAFANA_INSTANCE
go to connections -> Add new connections -> search and select infinity -> add new connection on the top right
For the token ->
ADMINISTRATION > USERS AND ACCESS > SERVICE ACCOUNTS
CLICK ON CREATE NEW SERVICE ACCOUNT
Give it a name,assign it to ADMIN Role and create it
on that account create an account token                                      secrets GRAFANA_TOKEN

